'''Jane Busby''' is the actress who played [[Chief]] [[Chirpa]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]'' ''and an Ugnaught in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']].

Busby, an English woman, has also appeared in a chapter of the TV series [[Wikipedia:Doctor Who|''Doctor Who'']] in [[1988]].

